South African actor Zamani Mbatha. Image supplied JOHANNESBURG - South African actor, Zamani Ndlovu has secured a role on the popular e.tv soapie, Rhythm City. READ: Mmabatho Montsho's film wins international award Mbatha will be making his debut on the show as Suffocate's adoptive son, Pule Ndlovu Catch Mbatha as Ndlovu from Wednesday, 18 November, at 7:00 pm on e.tv.